data.description: Exceptional back yard pool home, great for entertaining. Pool features include water falls, water features, slides, kiddie pool, large spa with swim up to bar with sunken BBQ & covered patio with fan. This home has 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms with one bedroom and adjacent bathroom down stairs.  Double entry doors opens to a beautiful spiral staircase with vaulted ceiling. Kitchen has plenty of cabinet space with pantry. Open floor plan to family room with fireplace and view of pool. Living room with formal dining room. Plantation shutters throughout the home. Downstairs laundry room to 3 car finished garage with plenty of storage. Large main bedroom with vaulted ceiling, fireplace and private balcony over looking the waterfall pool. 2 walk in closets in bathroom with stand alone tub and shower and dual vanities. An additional 3 bedrooms upstairs with a sharable bathroom. This home has A/C dual unit and Attic fan. RV parking on the side with plenty of storage. This home is a must see!
